cast.overview: Matilda Wormwood is an exquisite and intelligent little girl. Unfortunately, her parents, Harry and Zinnia misunderstand her because they think she is so different. As time passes, she finally starts school and has a kind teacher, loyal friends, and a sadistic headmistress. As she gets fed up with the constant cruelty, she begins to realize that she has a gift of telekinetic powers. After some days of practice, she suddenly turns the tables to stand up to Harry and Zinnia and outwit the headmistress.
cast.title: Matilda

details.biography: Christel was born and raised in Los Angeles and developed a love for acting at a young age. She began working on various projects which resulted in landing a regular role as Lily Winters on The Young and the Restless in 2002, for which she won a Daytime Emmy. In addition to acting, she is expanding her craft by creating and producing content.
details.name: Christel Khalil
